(6, 1, '2016-02-22 12:30:38', '2016-02-22 12:30:38', 'It is well recognized that one way to communicate with a person via dream is leave an audio message in the person‚Äôs subconscious mind. From there, the dreaming mind will manifest the message into the dreamscape. The person‚Äôs ability to interpret the message depends on the capacity of their conscious mind to receive from the unconscious. - See more at: http://www.drwattz.com/the-dream-phone/#comments\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-7" src="http://wordpress-tutorial/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/dream-phone-1024x652-300x191.png" alt="dream-phone-1024x652" width="300" height="191" />\r\n\r\nTo use:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Load coffee beans</li>\r\n	<li>Dial number to grind beans</li>\r\n	<li>Leave dream message</li>\r\n	<li>Hang up to start brewing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Warning</strong>: If the users of the machine does not drink the coffee there is a possibility the person dreaming will not wake up from their dream.\r\n\r\n<em>Notes: Apparently while sleepwalking, I brewed coffee and called myself. Interesting outcomes ensued.</em>\r\n\r\n- See more at: http://www.drwattz.com/the-dream-phone/#comments', 'The Dream Phone', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-dream-phone', '', '', '2016-02-22 13:05:14', '2016-02-22 13:05:14', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/?p=6', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(7, 1, '2016-02-22 12:29:32', '2016-02-22 12:29:32', '', 'Dream Phone', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dream-phone-1024x652', '', '', '2016-02-22 13:21:33', '2016-02-22 13:21:33', '', 6, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/dream-phone-1024x652.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(8, 1, '2016-02-22 12:30:38', '2016-02-22 12:30:38', 'It is well recognized that one way to communicate with a person via dream is leave an audio message in the person‚Äôs subconscious mind. From there, the dreaming mind will manifest the message into the dreamscape. The person‚Äôs ability to interpret the message depends on the capacity of their conscious mind to receive from the unconscious. - See more at: http://www.drwattz.com/the-dream-phone/#comments\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-7" src="http://wordpress-tutorial/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/dream-phone-1024x652-300x191.png" alt="dream-phone-1024x652" width="300" height="191" />\r\n\r\nTo use:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Load coffee beans</li>\r\n	<li>Dial number to grind beans</li>\r\n	<li>Leave dream message</li>\r\n	<li>Hang up to start brewing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Warning</strong>: If the users of the machine does not drink the coffee there is a possibility the person dreaming will not wake up from their dream.\r\n\r\n<em>Notes: Apparently while sleepwalking, I brewed coffee and called myself. Interesting outcomes ensued.</em>\r\n\r\n- See more at: http://www.drwattz.com/the-dream-phone/#comments', 'The Dream Phone', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-22 12:30:38', '2016-02-22 12:30:38', '', 6, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/2016/02/22/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2016-02-22 12:31:58', '2016-02-22 12:31:58', 'In order to transport to one of the 141 dimensions of pure emotion, one only has to put on the Interdimensional Mood Ring while experiencing a particular emotion. He or she will immediately be transported to the world of emotion corresponding to the mood felt at the time of putting on the ring. The person will enter the world stripped of awareness of and body, mind, and ego and will remain in the world until he or she wishes to experience another emotion. - See more at:\r\n\r\n<strong>Warning:</strong> A potential does exist for the inverse to be true. An emotional dimension could, in theory, enter into the person and manifest as a pure emotion in human form. It is unclear how long this effect could last for or how to reverse it. Likely, removing the ring would work. - See more at:', 'Interdimensional Mood Ring', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interdimensional-mood-ring', '', '', '2016-02-22 13:06:58', '2016-02-22 13:06:58', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/?p=9', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2016-02-22 12:31:58', '2016-02-22 12:31:58', 'In order to transport to one of the 141 dimensions of pure emotion, one only has to put on the Interdimensional Mood Ring while experiencing a particular emotion. He or she will immediately be transported to the world of emotion corresponding to the mood felt at the time of putting on the ring. The person will enter the world stripped of awareness of and body, mind, and ego and will remain in the world until he or she wishes to experience another emotion. - See more at:\r\n\r\n<strong>Warning:</strong> A potential does exist for the inverse to be true. An emotional dimension could, in theory, enter into the person and manifest as a pure emotion in human form. It is unclear how long this effect could last for or how to reverse it. Likely, removing the ring would work. - See more at:', 'Interdimensional Mood Ring', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-22 12:31:58', '2016-02-22 12:31:58', '', 9, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/2016/02/22/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2016-02-22 12:32:47', '2016-02-22 12:32:47', 'In order to ensure that creativity remains accessible to the world, I channeled a direct connection to the dimension of creativity and stored it as an electrical current in the frame of these glasses. When the frames are placed on the face, an electrical current of creativity is completed that passes through the pineal gland of the person wearing the glasses.\r\n\r\nThe effect rendered allows the wearer to see infinite creative the world around them. When the glasses are removed, the wearer will not be able to put into words what was seen and will likely not be able to speak at all for a period of time. However, over time the person will express their experience through a heightened state of their own creativity.\r\n\r\n<em>Note: For some unknown reason, the completed electrical circuit makes the wearer unseeable to anyone in our universe not also wearing creativity invisibility glasses.</em>', 'Creativity Invisibility Glasses', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'creativity-invisibility-glasses', '', '', '2016-02-22 13:05:49', '2016-02-22 13:05:49', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/?p=11', 0, 'post', '', 4),
(12, 1, '2016-02-22 12:32:47', '2016-02-22 12:32:47', 'In order to ensure that creativity remains accessible to the world, I channeled a direct connection to the dimension of creativity and stored it as an electrical current in the frame of these glasses. When the frames are placed on the face, an electrical current of creativity is completed that passes through the pineal gland of the person wearing the glasses.\r\n\r\nThe effect rendered allows the wearer to see infinite creative the world around them. When the glasses are removed, the wearer will not be able to put into words what was seen and will likely not be able to speak at all for a period of time. However, over time the person will express their experience through a heightened state of their own creativity.\r\n\r\n<em>Note: For some unknown reason, the completed electrical circuit makes the wearer unseeable to anyone in our universe not also wearing creativity invisibility glasses.</em>', 'Creativity Invisibility Glasses', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-22 12:32:47', '2016-02-22 12:32:47', '', 11, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/2016/02/22/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(15, 1, '2016-02-22 13:14:32', '2016-02-22 13:14:32', 'Welcome! I am Dr. Plank Wattz and this is my web site for talking about my inventions and research.\r\n\r\nMost of my work has to do with inter-dimensional interactivity and it‚Äôs relationship to human consciousness and creativity.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in any of my inventions, please leave a comment!\r\n\r\n- See more at: http://www.drwattz.com/about-dr-wattz/#sthash.iDAWaZif.dpuf', 'About Dr. Wattz', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-dr-wattz', '', '', '2016-02-22 13:15:16', '2016-02-22 13:15:16', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-tutorial/?page_id=15', 0, 'page', '', 0),
