(4, 1, 'description', 'Hello everyone,\r\n\r\nI am an enthusiast Junior Web Developer, computers being passion since childhood. Up until a few months ago, I was more hardware oriented (doing it part-time, as a hobby), although I was always intrigued about how the www and it''s websites work. \r\nFeeling that what I currently do doesn''t really reflect my personality, I decided to take some private class in my hometown. It was a great decision, as it opened this new and fascinating world for me in such a way, that I decideed I want it to become my career path. \r\nSo my first step was to enter the front door and start with Front-End Development as a niche, but in the future, I plan to learn Back-End Developemnt aswell. We''ll see what the future brings, but for now I am looking to accumulate experience in my new field.'),
